dcterms:description: The 'Muddy Yard' scenario features an outdoor area with two muddy sections and an outdoor mat, as well as an indoor area with a sink. The scenario is modeled as a Kripke structure with a set of states and labels, and various LTL rules are applied to analyze agent behavior.
